5812 - Eating Places Summary > TAP ENERGY (THAILAND) PTY LTD (formerly TAP ENERGY (THAILAND) PTY LTD) is an Australian proprietary company. Its operations cover eating places. The company is not involved in the import or export of goods. TAP ENERGY (THAILAND) PTY LTD is headquartered in West Perth, Western Australia. It is headed by director Troy John Hayden. For the 2024 financial year, the company reported revenue of USD34.83 million. Its net profit totalled USD5.51 million. TAP ENERGY (THAILAND) PTY LTD forms part of the retail trade industry sector.
